ed1c4f39-0cfd-42d9-814b-969e6d18251d.title: Note
ed1c4f39-0cfd-42d9-814b-969e6d18251d.text: Not sure if TALK_TO_OSMAN should go to during.

088c3f94-83e1-4269-8c30-ad064e423187.title: Hassan
088c3f94-83e1-4269-8c30-ad064e423187.text:
Greetings I am Hassan, Chancellor to the Emir of Al-
Kharid.

options.text: Can I help you? You must need some help here in the desert.
It's just too hot here. How can you stand it?
Do you mind if I just kill your warriors?

61e646a0-2622-4cee-aca2-5378f8b52523.title: <player>
61e646a0-2622-4cee-aca2-5378f8b52523.text:
Can I help you? You must need some help here in the
desert.

8d5289e6-9ad3-451a-a9b8-ff0f1aed3425.title: Hassan
8d5289e6-9ad3-451a-a9b8-ff0f1aed3425.text:
I need the services of someone, yes. If you are
interested, see the spymaster, Osman. I manage the
finances here. Come to me when you need payment.

3faec923-6653-4db1-b79c-e0637c1237fd.title: <player>
3faec923-6653-4db1-b79c-e0637c1237fd.text: It's just too hot here. How can you stand it?

8df4787b-d19a-4799-9524-fcc07796d7f7.title: Hassan
8df4787b-d19a-4799-9524-fcc07796d7f7.text:
We manage, in our humble way. We are a wealthy
town and we have water. It cures many thirsts.

02496bf8-eb40-4f5a-b890-c7b688683de7.title: <player>
02496bf8-eb40-4f5a-b890-c7b688683de7.text: Do you mind if I just kill your warriors?

4f034d40-8b5b-4518-a1bb-546c998b9475.title: Hassan
4f034d40-8b5b-4518-a1bb-546c998b9475.text:
You are welcome. They are not expensive. We have
them here to stop the elite guard being bothered. They
are a little harder to kill.

af206ad1-f9ba-447d-aefb-d3dd531c58ec.title: Hassan
af206ad1-f9ba-447d-aefb-d3dd531c58ec.text:
I understand the Spymaster has hired you. I will pay
the reward only when the Prince is rescued.

33cdaa91-3f20-47a1-88a7-92c599441796.title: Hassan
33cdaa91-3f20-47a1-88a7-92c599441796.text:
You have the eternal gratitude of the Emir for
rescuing his son. I am authorised to pay you 700
coins.

ccd20b5e-774d-48fc-bcaf-1653a5fb5013.title: Hassan
ccd20b5e-774d-48fc-bcaf-1653a5fb5013.text:
You are a friend of the town of Al-Kharid. If we have
more tasks to complete, we will ask you. Please, keep in
contact. Good employees are not easy to find.
